ISS Specter
The ISS Specter is the covert operative branch of the Coalition's Internal
Security Specialists. Where Peacekeepers maintain order openly, Specters work
without uniforms, gathering intelligence and conducting operations that the
Coalition will never officially acknowledge.

ISS Specters choose from Espionage, Rogue, Military, and Technical skill
categories. They are experts in surveillance, infiltration, disguise, and
wetwork. They answer to ISS command directly and operate outside normal
Coalition chains of command.

Attribute requirements: IQ 11, ME 10, MA 10, PP 11.
Starting equipment: Civilian clothing in multiple styles, a concealed laser
pistol, encrypted communicator, forged multi-faction identity documents, and
a small personal fund for operational expenses.
